Required Package:
-------------------
1.redux 
2.react-redux 
3.redux-devtool-extension 

Crome - redux Dev Tool extension 

=================================

Step 1 : React Component - dispatch an redux action 
Step 2 : Redux Action to redux reducer 
Step 3 : Reducer is going to update store, based action type 

Step 4: once store is updated, It reflect back to view 

How to displatch an action?